<text top="324" left="77" width="467" height="13" font="2">For an antibody to meet ENCODE validation standards, a single band of the predicted </text>
<text top="338" left="77" width="467" height="13" font="2">size,  or  a  band  of  no  less  than  half  the  total  signal,  must  be  detected  in  a  lane  on  a </text>
<text top="351" left="77" width="74" height="13" font="2">Western blot. </text>
<text top="375" left="77" width="3" height="13" font="2"> </text>
